msgid ""
"If ``getenforce`` returns anything other than ``Enforcing``, run "
"``setenforce Enforcing`` or otherwise configure SELinux by editing "
"``/etc/selinux/config`` and rebooting until SELinux is enforcing."
msgstr ""

